flowRoot.flowPara: ⦁ Tear the pieces on the dotted lines
⦁ Place the flag and tee box far apart
⦁ Place other business cards to mark water hazards
⦁ Players take turns flicking their golf ball towards the flag starting at the tee box
⦁ If the ball falls off the table or goes into the water put it back to where it was flicked from and that counts as two flicks
⦁ Lowest number of flicks to reach the flag wins!
